      "content": "i get that, but i already have the pills here and i'm just so exhausted. i don't really want to wait until my next appointment to see if it works. since melatonin is just a natural supplement and zolpidem is a medicine, wouldn't they just kind of work together to make me sleepy? like, would they really interact in a dangerous way or is it just a precaution?",
